# Google Maps Embed API key — powers the "Areas We Serve" maps.
# The legacy keyless embed was deprecated by Google (now blocks framing), so a
# key is required. It is exposed in the iframe src (expected for Embed API
# keys); in the Google Cloud console restrict it to:
#   - API:      "Maps Embed API" only
#   - Referrer: https://www.riverbirchtreeservice.com/*  (and the www/apex)
# Copy this file to `.env` (gitignored) and paste the key. Rebuild to apply.
PUBLIC_GOOGLE_MAPS_KEY=
